Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.39,0:00:03.54,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.40,0:00:07.59,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,A handmade tea cozy to keep the tea warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:11.21,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Now we can have warm black tea anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.82,0:00:13.22,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,It's round...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.22,0:00:15.11,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,And a little chubby...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.11,0:00:15.97,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,We can call you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.78,0:00:17.64,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Pukkun?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:19.22,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Pukkun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.66,0:00:22.27,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,It's like it's alive. That's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:24.42,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Do your best, Pukkun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.67,0:00:27.92,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Pukkun! Pukkun! Pukkun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.17,0:00:29.50,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:37.15,hc_opening_jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}nakushita yakusoku wa hoshi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:37.15,hc_opening_eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}Send the lost promises to the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:43.52,hc_opening_jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}omoide wa tokenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:43.52,hc_opening_eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}My memories won't fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.03,0:00:58.20,hc_opening_jap,,0,0,0,,yotsuba no clover sagashinagara kimi no kao
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.03,0:00:58.20,hc_opening_eng,,0,0,0,,I steal a glance at you as we look for four-leaf clovers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.37,0:01:04.44,hc_opening_jap,,0,0,0,,chirari nusumi mite wa me o sorasu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.37,0:01:04.44,hc_opening_eng,,0,0,0,,But then divert my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.88,0:01:09.88,hc_opening_jap,,0,0,0,,yasashii ame wa furu watashitachi no ue ni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.88,0:01:09.88,hc_opening_eng,,0,0,0,,The gentle rain falls above our heads
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.88,0:01:15.42,hc_opening_jap,,0,0,0,,surechigau hito no kazu dake dramatic ni naru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.88,0:01:15.42,hc_opening_eng,,0,0,0,,as it becomes as dramatic as the number of people passing by
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.72,0:01:20.89,hc_opening_jap,,0,0,0,,kowareta taisetsu na mono to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.72,0:01:20.89,hc_opening_eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder if we'll ever be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.26,0:01:27.23,hc_opening_jap,,0,0,0,,itsuka mata aeru hi ga kurukashira
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.26,0:01:27.23,hc_opening_eng,,0,0,0,,reunite with those precious things that were broken
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.50,0:01:32.54,hc_opening_jap,,0,0,0,,nokoshita kizuato ga kienai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.50,0:01:32.54,hc_opening_eng,,0,0,0,,The scars that were left behind won't go away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:38.24,hc_opening_jap,,0,0,0,,sorezore no basho made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:38.24,hc_opening_eng,,0,0,0,,Now we must depart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.71,0:01:41.98,hc_opening_jap,,0,0,0,,mou ikanakucha
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.71,0:01:41.98,hc_opening_eng,,0,0,0,,To our own separate ways
