Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.96,0:02:16.36,hc_alternative,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:23.28,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I didn't spend money for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:21.41,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\bord1.2\fscx65\fs29\fsp5\3c&HECFCFE&\c&H1889D4&\frz7.103\pos(305,155)}Get a hold of yourself, Miwako-san
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:25.60,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,What's Miwako-san crying over?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:28.43,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,This, Takaido-san. This, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.84,0:02:30.56,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,What is this, a men's magazine?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:32.69,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,That's Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:38.78,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,But he's wearing a ridiculous shirt! And they're\Ncalling him a master of fashion?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:40.99,hc_fo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Title: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Snapshots of fashion masters in different cities
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:39.78,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:41.36,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.73,0:02:45.24,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,The truth is that when we went to Asakusa-bashi for business...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:49.43,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,...she found a ridiculously "fashionable" clothing\Nstore and saw this outfit in the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:50.28,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Wow! Look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:56.38,hc_fo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(363,77)\i1\fnTimes New Roman\b0\bord1.5\be1\shad0\3c&H8DE0EA&\c&H4A7579&}Ayakusa\NMiyoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:56.38,hc_fo,,0,0,0,,{\i1\bord0.1\be1\shad0\pos(673,25)\c&H819092&\3c&H819092&}Men's Fashion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:54.13,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,This design is ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.13,0:02:55.92,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,How very fashionable...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.38,0:03:03.88,hc_fo,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\be1\shad0\fs15\pos(260,215)\3c&HC6DBF5&\c&H54637B&}Evil
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:03:00.49,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,{\an8}M-Miwako-san, is this really for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:03:02.82,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,It had such an impact on her that she decided\Nto buy it for Yamazaki's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.11,0:03:03.12,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's fine, just wear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.42,0:03:06.39,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Even though she gave it to him as a prank...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.92,0:03:08.56,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Miwako-san, how do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:09.81,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:12.06,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,He managed to look great in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:14.33,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:21.72,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No fun! No fun! No fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:18.44,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,On top of that, he was featured in a\Nmagazine as a master of fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:22.74,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,So, she wanted to embarrass Yamazaki but\Nended up boosting his confidence instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:24.82,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:29.20,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow I'm going to Nakano! Right on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:36.25,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Here, Yamazaki. I got you a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.78,0:03:38.46,hc_fo,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fnTimes New Roman\b0\fscx70\pos(231,386)\frz25.32\frx352\fry356\c&H2A2F30&}Nakano Hollywood
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:38.46,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,It's a T-shirt! Please try it on for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.63,0:03:43.05,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,But I only just got a wonderful shirt from you the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.29,0:03:44.93,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,No worries, just try it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:46.26,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)\bord0\shad0\fnTimes New Roman\b0\fscy80\pos(407,171)\frz1.874\c&H787C87&}Evil
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:54.10,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Um, I... t-this thing has a picture of a robot on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:57.10,hc_fo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,0)\bord0.5\be1\shad0\fnTimes New Roman\b0\fscy80\pos(463,157)\frz330.387\3c&HCCD6E7&\c&H565A62&}Evil
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:54.94,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.43,0:03:57.10,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Um... I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:03:59.03,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.07,0:04:03.13,hc_fo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)\bord0\shad0\c&H3B4444&\fs50\fscx65\pos(387,337)}Next mont{\fsp15}h...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.31,0:04:07.78,hc_fo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\pos(139,92)\bord0.1\shad2\be1\c&H7292EA&\fscx80\4c&H515151&\3c&H515151&}The fashion master who\Nsmoothly displays\Na bold anime design!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.31,0:04:07.78,hc_fo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\bord2\be1\shad0\fs30\fscx80\4c&H515151&\pos(512,70)\c&H6F7171&\3c&HEDF2F1&}This is the {\c&H4CD194&}relaxed {\c&H6F7171&}look that {\c&HF8C1AB&}moves\Naway{\c&H6F7171&} a little bit from maturity!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:09.47,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:09.98,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\an7\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\bord1.2\fscx65\fs22\fsp3\3c&HECFCFE&\frz19.218\c&H3C9FD3&\pos(20,147)}Aww~~\N\h\h\h\hMiwako-san, get a hold of yourself ~~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:14.54,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,He's looking good in that knockoff Mazindaiger X T-shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:17.54,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,He does it flawlessly, like it's second nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:20.63,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I'll go ahead and drop off these materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:25.43,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Miwako-san, maybe you should just give up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:33.18,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say, he's really stylish, so he'll\Nlook good in almost anything you make him wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:34.27,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:36.56,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I must accept his challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:36.56,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,0)\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx65\fs29\fsp5\3c&HECFCFE&\c&H2790D5&\pos(220,341)\frz30.533}Please don't lose\NMiwako-san
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:39.73,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,All right, on my next business trip to Izu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.97,0:04:43.27,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,It's no use. Her eyes are already a different color.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.56,0:04:47.82,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Just you watch, Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.61,0:04:53.53,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki! I bought this present in Izu for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:55.50,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Miwako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.62,0:04:57.62,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,He's in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:04:59.62,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:01.55,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Miwako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:03.25,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,He's in there again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:03.25,hc_fo,,0,0,0,,{\frz8.767\frx352\fry2\pos(684,147)\bord0.6\fs33\shad0\be1\c&H91B891&}Fashion\NLead
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:04.96,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:07.26,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Miwako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:08.93,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,He's in there again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:10.85,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,He's more or less a regular...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:13.27,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Is he their exclusive model or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.59,0:05:15.89,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Miwako-san, maybe you should just give up already...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:16.94,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:20.44,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,We have a business trip to Nagoya together\Nnext week, don't we, Nomiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.18,0:05:25.15,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,All right, Nomiya!
