Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:28.45,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Let's find a dilapidated and "fashionable" shopping district quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:31.87,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Aw, they're all closed already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:33.75,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Well, it's already past 9PM after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:39.71,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,But we start work at 9AM tomorrow and\Nneed to be on the bullet train by 5PM...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.49,0:05:44.84,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,So, we need to at least get an idea tonight of where\Nthey might sell the bits and odds we're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.16,0:05:47.26,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Oh, my! I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:48.72,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Nomiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.04,0:05:50.26,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Why have you become so cooperative?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:55.00,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Kaneko-san from accounting asked me to end this ordeal already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.21,0:05:57.10,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Save me, Nomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:05:58.92,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I'll get scolded by the tax accountant!
