Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.44,0:06:05.14,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I can't pass these receipts from mysterious\Nretail stores as company expenses!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:06.99,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:08.64,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.32,0:06:11.30,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,But hey, this is a battle, so...
