Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:13.86,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. Let's find the place already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:18.66,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Nomiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:20.41,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Miwako-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:21.42,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,That!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:25.07,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,T-This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:26.20,hc_fo,,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Signs: {\be1\3c&HB27E5B&\fs22}The Expert Fashion Store for Pure Men {\3c&HC09C73&\fs27} — Wada\N{\3c&H2A1B0E&\fs22}The Expert Fashion Store for Pure Men\N{\3c&H4F2618&\fs27}Dandy House  — {\fs22}Open{\3c&H563621&} til 8PM
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:28.49,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,"D-Dandy House"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.79,0:06:29.82,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,On top of that, "Wada"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:33.54,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Both in terms of what this storefront looks like\Nand how the paint is peeling off the sign...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:34.76,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,This place is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.96,0:06:36.26,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Awesome as always, Nomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.67,0:06:39.33,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}Looks like we've already won the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.26,0:06:37.09,hc_fo,,0,0,0,,{\frz353.684\fnTimes New Roman\b0\fscx80\bord0\shad0\fsp-1\c&H28150A&\move(153,228,153,552)\frx10\fry10}First\NDistrict
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.72,0:06:44.36,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,We'll fax you the official estimates tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:48.03,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Please say hello to Mario-kun and Luigi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:52.66,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,We have three hours until we need to catch the bullet train.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.02,0:06:54.62,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,That's more than enough time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:57.33,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Just you wait, Dandy House Wada!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:06:58.79,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,And you too, Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:04.62,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\shad0\3c&H54B1E0&\c&H32617E&\fs22\bord1\be1\fscy80\fsp-2\move(30,36,70,36)}Summer Clothes\NLowest Prices On
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:04.62,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\shad0\3c&H54B1E0&\c&H32617E&\fs22\bord1\be1\fscy80\fsp-2\move(370,34,410,34)}Now In Stock\NWinter Clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:05.88,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,How's this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:07.71,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Looks like a laminated captain's shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.71,0:07:09.55,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,That's nice! How much is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:11.34,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Pricey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:13.05,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,13,000 yen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:16.10,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,This kind of attire is expensive for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:20.26,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,That polo shirt over there is 28,900 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.84,0:07:27.05,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Say, Nomiya. Isn't this polo shirt with the tiger on it better?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:29.32,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,It's a jaguar, and anyway, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:30.95,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,It's too expensive for just a challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:35.74,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,But to finish him off for sure, this animal print is more...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.74,0:07:37.79,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,It's 28,900 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:44.07,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,But... I came all the way to Nagoya, and I can't\Ncome back here even if I wanted to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:48.21,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Miwako-san, please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:53.38,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,First of all, what will you do if you spend all that\Nmoney and it actually looks good on him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:56.13,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,G-Good point...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.13,0:08:00.64,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine. This shirt is horrible enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:03.48,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:09.36,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,How embarrassing... it's such a bold design!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:12.59,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hello, is this Dandy House Wada in Nagoya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.06,0:08:16.43,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,It looks good on him... Yeah, it looks great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.06,0:08:14.93,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'd like to place a telephone order.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:17.32,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'll deposit the money immediately, so\Nplease have it delivered tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:20.75,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Delivery!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:21.95,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.28,0:08:27.54,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is it! I should have gotten this in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:29.55,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Is this okay, Nomiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:33.22,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm kind of feeling sorry for Yamazaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:36.72,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Well, at this point, we have no choice but\Nto let her continue until she's satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:39.34,hc_fo,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&H3B4444&\fs50\fscx65\pos(499,340)}But next mont{\fsp15}h...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:47.79,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,T-T-T-T-The 28,900 yen...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.51,0:08:48.52,hc_fo,,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Title:{\3c&H5ACBA4&} Announcing the National Fashion Champion!!\N{\3c&H4655A0&}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hCaptured while working in the neighborhood\N{\3c&HC9AE8E&}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hA stylish adult who can boldly wear an unconventional design
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:50.73,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:52.28,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.14,0:08:54.97,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Miwako-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:56.78,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Miwako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:09:00.41,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,P-Please get a hold of yourself, Miwako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:08.50,hc_alternative,,0,0,0,,In the end, instead of embarrassing him,\Nwe made him into a fashion champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.87,0:09:11.00,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Miwako-san, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:14.80,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Please swap this towel with another cold one...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:16.86,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's anemia...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:18.57,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I want to eat ice cream...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.89,0:09:21.33,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Pistachio, right? I've already bought some.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:25.85,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Please, ask for anything. I'll be here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.85,0:09:27.34,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Ice cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:28.39,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:34.78,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,"Actually, most of these clothes were picked\Nout for me by a senpai at work...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.89,0:09:36.32,hc_fo,,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&\fad(850,0)}Content: {\3c&H7DD8F6&}A Comment from the Champion\N{\3c&H43474A&}\h\h\h\h\hTokyo / Yamazaki Kazushi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.44,0:09:38.72,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I went to an all-boys high school and studied at a science and\Nengineering college, so I was always surrounded by guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:40.87,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,...meaning I was never fashionable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:43.66,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Thus, I'm really grateful for my senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:47.54,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm currently in a one-sided love with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:52.17,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I want to become respectable and make a\Nmove on her, so I'll do my best at work!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.24,0:09:54.42,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Yamazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.12,0:09:56.38,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I apologize, Yamazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:09:59.01,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I hadn't noticed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.00,0:10:02.43,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I'll try to help you more from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.67,0:10:05.98,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,But for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:08.94,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,We're going on a business trip to Osaka next!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:09.93,hc_fo,,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Box: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Yamazaki Fund
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:09.93,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.86,0:10:14.15,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll go with the more interesting one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.52,0:10:26.39,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,700)\bord0\shad0\fscx80\fs35\c&H4D4D4D&\pos(427,101)}This is the story of what happened with Mayama-kun & co. right around when Morita-kun came back from the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.78,0:10:31.49,hc_fo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)\bord1\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fscy80\fs70\b0\shad0\be1\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&HA53BB3&\pos(676,370)}Hmph
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:35.07,hc_fo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fscy80\shad0\fs50\b0\c&HA53BB3&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(664,351)}This is my
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:35.07,hc_fo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fscy80\shad0\fs50\b0\c&HA53BB3&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(177,374)}only part
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:38.80,hc_fo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fscy80\shad0\fs50\b0\c&HA53BB3&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(673,346)}Why don't you\Nhurry up
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:38.80,hc_fo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fscy80\shad0\fs50\b0\c&HA53BB3&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(173,430)}and continue\Nwith the story?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:40.45,hc_fo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,700)\fnTimes New Roman\bord2.5\fscx70\fsp3\shad0\fs70\b0\c&H32322B&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(389,416)}Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.35,0:10:47.52,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Bear in hole strategy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.97,0:10:49.85,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,This makes my defense perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:51.56,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Attack me from anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:55.07,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,When you place your defense like that, the game lasts forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.64,0:10:57.03,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.57,0:11:00.28,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm only doing what you always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.98,0:11:03.99,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,But you sure improve quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.74,0:11:07.16,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I only taught you how to play the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.45,0:11:08.95,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I practice every day, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:16.17,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,But gosh... I never imagined shogi could be this fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:19.01,hc_alternative,,0,0,0,,Now that he can work with Rika again...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:25.10,hc_alternative,,0,0,0,,It's like the time and energy that had been allocated\Nto stalking her has all been converted towards shogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:28.89,hc_alternative,,0,0,0,,And here I thought I was pretty good at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.43,0:11:33.40,hc_alternative,,0,0,0,,He's prone to obsessing over things to begin with, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:41.82,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, you're still in your twenties. Don't you have\Nbetter things to do after work than play shogi with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.15,0:11:43.02,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't you get invited out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.27,0:11:47.23,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Invited...? Well, sometimes I get invited to date parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.15,0:11:50.29,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,The love antics of the youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:51.96,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I've never been to one myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:53.54,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,It must be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.54,0:11:54.29,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't you ever go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.70,0:11:58.33,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I've long grown out of such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:02.47,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I went to plenty in my younger days,\Nso I figure I've had my fair share.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.12,0:12:06.64,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mayama-kun. Shall we fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:08.29,hc_fo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fscy90\shad0\b0\fs50\be1\c&H8C8F93&\3c&HEEF0F0&\pos(240,368)\bord2}20's
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:08.29,hc_fo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fscy90\shad0\b0\fs50\be1\c&H8C8F93&\3c&HEEF0F0&\bord2\pos(745,270)}30's
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:12.52,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Are you guys playing shogi together again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:13.81,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takemoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:17.11,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Are you taking a break, Hagu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:20.07,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Takemoto, Hagu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:22.15,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Do you guys want some roll cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:23.86,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Yes, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:27.99,hc_fo,,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Cup: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Hanamoto Hagumi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:30.20,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,That's right. Hagu-chan, are you interested\Nin things like date parties?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:35.67,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a sec, Mayama-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.07,0:12:37.17,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,What is this all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.45,0:12:38.96,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Please don't say anything weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.41,0:12:41.84,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Hagu-chan can't handle this! Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:43.88,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I, um, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:45.62,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I just thought I'd ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.62,0:12:49.51,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Man, it's always been such a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.51,0:12:54.35,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Hagu's always been uncomfortable around new\Npeople, and even as a college student now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:12:57.94,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,He doesn't think it's a problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:57.94,hc_fo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(260,370)\bord0\shad0\c&H38393F&}Comedy of the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:04.40,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,On that topic, I don't hear much about\NYamada-san's date parties either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.85,0:13:08.28,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,She's so pretty, I bet she gets invited all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:11.73,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Oh... about Yamada...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.73,0:13:14.00,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Huh? Did I just step on a landmine?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:16.49,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.49,0:13:17.58,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,You go to Hamabi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:20.62,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Hey, there's a girl named Yamada in the\Nceramics department, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:23.71,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Ah... y-yes, sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,0:13:27.26,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Rather, it was me who stepped on the landmine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:31.26,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,H-How do you do, I'm Yamada Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:32.34,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.59,0:13:34.43,hc_alternative,,0,0,0,,S-So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.05,0:13:37.94,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Um, stewed giblets and grilled mackerel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:46.32,hc_fo,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fscx70\bord0.5\be1\c&H313D48&\fs22\move(244,418,507,418)\3c&H4B635F&}Menu
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:39.77,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Grilled chicken skin and grilled smelt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.76,0:13:41.26,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Fish cake and miso-sauteed eggplant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:46.32,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Oh! And bacon-wrapped asparagus. Oh, and also...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:46.32,hc_alternative,,0,0,0,,She eats a lot! But she's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:49.24,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,We were her classmates in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.69,0:13:52.12,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I mean, isn't she just so pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.69,0:13:54.91,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Even so, she was persistently in an unrequited love...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.28,0:13:58.42,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,She was saying how she couldn't think of anyone but him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:14:01.09,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,So, we invited her to a date party...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.49,0:14:03.67,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,...thinking that it'd be fine since she wouldn't be competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.99,0:14:06.34,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,We thought it'd be a way to get more guys to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:08.63,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:13.60,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Why... why won't that idiot even look back at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:16.14,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm just in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:20.13,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Damn it, how can he not realize Yamada-san's beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:21.86,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I'll murder that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:25.51,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I guess... crude girls aren't good enough for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:28.36,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,No! You're so cute, Yamada-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:30.70,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I will wait for you forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.98,0:14:35.73,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Yamada-san! Please have some water!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:37.94,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Before you knew it, it was a Yamada harem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:43.67,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Then the guys who were completely enslaved\Nby her beauty never stopped calling her...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.03,0:14:49.34,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Wreaking havoc on the date party scene, Yamada laid\Nwaste to numerous battlefields all over the place...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:51.47,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,In the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:15:09.02,hc_fo,,0,0,0,,{\fnAlsina Ultrajada\b0\fscx80\fs33\shad0\bord2\be1\3c&HF4F6F2&\c&H41424A&\move(395,387,415,387)}A Mountain of Claims
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.08,0:14:55.54,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Please! Take that demon child off our hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:58.39,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Aren't you the guy that Yamada likes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.80,0:15:00.67,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Why isn't she good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:02.94,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Please settle down with her already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.14,0:15:09.02,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Girls like that came to me, one after another...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:12.86,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,And when I finally managed to shake them off and get away...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.02,0:15:19.04,hc_alternative,,0,0,0,,But stop showing up at socials and taking girls back\Nhome like they're takeout delivery, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:20.87,hc_alternative,,0,0,0,,How did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.11,0:15:25.13,hc_alternative,,0,0,0,,A friend of mine from another school has been\Nflooding me with questions about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.78,0:15:28.59,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Just like that, I was misunderstood by Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.58,0:15:35.30,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Thanks to that demon child, date parties\Nwere always a tragedy for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:38.97,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Y-Yamada-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:51.11,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Then, Mayama, aren't there any... fun events at work?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:59.62,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,There was a person who was into stuff like\Nthat before... in more ways than one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.07,0:16:01.29,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.07,0:16:04.17,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki was invited to a date party?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.74,0:16:09.24,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Moreover, by the girls from the editing department of the\Nfashion magazine that featured him as a champion?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.24,0:16:15.14,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,But... date parties are for people who\Nwant a boyfriend or girlfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:21.42,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,So although I'm honored that they invited me... that\Nis, there's someone else that I like right now, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.42,0:16:22.22,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,When is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.01,0:16:24.04,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,The day after tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.52,0:16:25.96,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Um... Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:25.06,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,That's soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.44,0:16:26.73,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,But don't you worry, Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:31.99,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I'll prepare the ultimate outfit for you, so that\Nyou won't lose out to those fashion gurus!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.31,0:16:34.20,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Give it up, Yamazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:38.85,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,There's not even a micron of wanting to prevent\Nyou from going to a date party in Miwako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.61,0:16:41.58,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\be1\fscx55\fs30\fsp5\3c&HECFCFE&\c&H2491D8&\frz6.475\pos(601,180)}Miwako-san, you're\Nkind of heating up ..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:41.58,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,In fact, she wants you to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.58,0:16:42.87,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,The place is Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.29,0:16:46.08,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,The people going are girls in their twenties and thirties.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:47.54,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,So it's black then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.99,0:16:51.59,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,We'll go with a tight black shirt and slender pants!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.83,0:16:56.66,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,D-Doesn't this make me look kind of like a host?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:16:59.54,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Worry not! You look wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.01,0:17:05.48,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,But it seems you are overdoing it a bit, so\Nlet's lighten it up with a lighter jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.97,0:17:08.34,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Here, isn't this jacket an unusual shade of green?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.89,0:17:10.40,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,To top off the get-up, wear this necktie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:15.15,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,A brilliant lemon-yellow to complement the green of your jacket!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.60,0:17:17.56,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Looks great.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.06,0:17:19.86,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,It looks great, Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:24.37,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,U-Um... Miwako-san, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:31.33,hc_fo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\fad(450,0)\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx55\fs27\fsp5\3c&HECFCFE&\c&H2491D8&\frz12.669\pos(222,127)}Whoa, as expected of\NMiwako-san's styling.\NYou look great!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:26.44,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Not bad. Not bad at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:28.96,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I think I have a future as a stylist!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:30.52,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.76,0:17:35.08,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Now then! I wonder how Yamazaki is doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:37.05,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Let's go sneak a peek!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:39.14,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,She's the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.67,0:17:41.01,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Devil indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:45.30,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm doing my very best right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:47.46,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,You're such a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:49.29,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Please take me away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:51.84,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Steal my precious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:55.69,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,That'd be too big for my pocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:17:59.87,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,W-Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:00.95,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,He's a hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.19,0:18:03.29,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Sister, let's give it up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.11,0:18:09.58,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,The way he is right now, he could be given\Na gold cross and still pull it off splendidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.26,0:18:19.42,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,What exactly do you want to do to Yamazaki anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:25.68,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,To belittle him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:29.81,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Then I want to point at him and laugh... and comfort him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:32.19,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,And then I want to be appreciated!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:36.99,hc_alternative,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki, are you really okay with this person?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.56,0:18:40.91,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Dance parties are kind of popular like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:43.95,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,T-To that Yamazaki guy, cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:46.48,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Let there be prosperity for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.90,0:18:52.67,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,But man... things just don't go the way we want them to, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:55.80,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Sensei, please don't put it so bleakly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.16,0:18:57.63,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,But don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:18:59.84,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Yeah, somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:02.30,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Things actually going right is a rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:06.59,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,This game of shogi that we're playing right now is a prime example!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.05,0:19:10.77,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,We've shored up our defenses so much\Nthat the game will never end...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:15.64,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Plus, whatever pieces we win we automatically place on defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.64,0:19:20.74,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,In shogi, the player's personality really\Ncomes to the forefront, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:23.74,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,It pains me to agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.98,0:19:26.54,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,You stress defense and prudence!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.98,0:19:27.86,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,You hate losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.65,0:19:32.65,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,How long has it been since we started playing, Mayama-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.53,0:19:38.46,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,It's already 1:30 in the morning, so it's\Nbeen about four and a half hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.46,0:19:42.34,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Seems like Hagu and Takemoto left without us noticing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.96,0:19:46.68,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Actually, haven't we been playing shogi until sunrise a lot recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.09,0:19:49.52,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,How about setting a time limit?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:50.39,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.88,0:19:52.68,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Like buying a competition clock?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.68,0:19:54.31,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Oh, that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.47,0:19:56.44,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,The one that tells you how much time you have left?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:19:58.73,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,But aren't they expensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:02.45,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,What we need right now is a way to allocate time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.77,0:20:05.78,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, we'll be stuck here forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.73,0:20:08.54,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,This is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.36,0:20:11.29,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,All right, Mayama-kun! Let's buy one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.53,0:20:13.04,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Yes, let's!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.33,0:20:16.63,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Y'know... wouldn't the problem be solved\Nif you guys just didn't stay up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:18.44,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,M-Morita!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:18.45,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Morita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.71,0:20:19.41,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.41,0:20:20.12,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Since when?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.12,0:20:22.25,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Just stop staying up so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:26.07,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Like I said, at your age, stop—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:27.55,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't say it, Morita! I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:29.25,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,You're making us seem like fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.25,0:20:31.60,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Like I was saying, at your age, isn't it stupid to—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.60,0:20:32.75,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:33.71,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Please don't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:36.63,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1400)}Stupid, stupid, stupid—!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:47.14,hc_ending_jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)}waratta kao ni tsukekomare
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:47.14,hc_ending_eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)}Taken advantage of by his smiling face
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:50.31,hc_ending_jap,,0,0,0,,kuchi ni shita sake ni aorarete, oh
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:50.31,hc_ending_eng,,0,0,0,,Stimulated by the alcohol she drank
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:53.27,hc_ending_jap,,0,0,0,,sora misereta toki ururunda face
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:53.27,hc_ending_eng,,0,0,0,,The tear that wells up when she's shown otherwise
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:56.98,hc_ending_jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}ki ga sukkari sono ki ni natteru
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:56.98,hc_ending_eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}She'd already become all for it
