Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:21:03.74,hc_ending_eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}Holding her head
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:05.45,hc_ending_jap,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(400,400)}atama kakaete
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:05.45,hc_ending_eng,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(400,400)}Holding her head
