Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:09.66,hc_ending_eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}Even if she tries to pretend that it was a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:15.46,hc_ending_jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}monogataru kare no paper
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:15.46,hc_ending_eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}His paper tells a different story
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:21.05,hc_ending_jap,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(400,400)}shiroku samete
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:21.05,hc_ending_eng,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(400,400)}Becoming white and discolored
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.04,0:21:26.43,hc_ending_jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)}kumo no ue nobori
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:26.43,hc_ending_eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)}Ascending above the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:32.73,hc_ending_jap,,0,0,0,,gin iro natsu tsunda yoru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:32.73,hc_ending_eng,,0,0,0,,The silvery summer's night she was picked up on
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.07,0:21:47.33,hc_ending_jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}shimetsukerareru mistake kienai
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.07,0:21:47.33,hc_ending_eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}She's being constricted by a mistake that won't go away
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.18,0:21:54.27,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Hagu-chan, Pukkun is really popular at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.85,0:21:55.73,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.19,0:21:59.52,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.84,0:22:01.57,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's your papa, Ayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.84,0:22:02.82,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.56,0:22:08.56,hc_alternative,,0,0,0,,T-That's—!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.44,0:22:11.12,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Ayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.85,0:22:13.16,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,I will treasure it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.83,0:22:18.21,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,But... don't you think this is a little too flashy for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.70,0:22:20.58,hc_standard,,0,0,0,,J-u-s-t kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.13,0:22:24.07,hc_alternative,,0,0,0,,Pukkun...
